snippet.title: The Engineer Update Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
-- Sorry, we didn't mean to insinuate anything by randomly uploading an older video to the TF2 channel. We are just doing some housekeeping, this video was previously only available in lower-res hosted on our servers and we wanted all of the videos to live in one place. --

A short look at the Engineer getting ready for his close-up. http://www.teamfortress.com/engineerupdate/. 

For more info visit www.teamfortress.com.
